The,IBM,Language,Identification,API,allows,developers,to,detect,the,language,of,any,text,sample,that,uses,UTF,character,encoding,This,API,is,offered,as,part,of,the,IBM,Watson,Developer,Cloud,which,is,hosted,on,the,Bluemix,platform,Sample,applications,using,the,API,with,Bluemix,are,provided,in,Java,Node,js,and,Ruby